<title>ALLTHE WAY TO CALVARY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Thagau tuomvel zan chuh a thim na e,
 Hukdampa lungkhamna a lien hi;
 A vak deihum in ka thagau a salh tieng,
 Thimna nawhmang in ei hukdam tai.

[V2]
 Kalvari lam chuh zuonin keidi'n a chieh,
 Keidi'n A chieh, keidi'n A chieh;
 Kalvari lam chuh zuonin keidi'n A chieh,
 Ka suokchak na'n A thii.

[V3]
 2. A masang ah gilo kithing in ka khu'n,
 A ngaihdam leh lungsiet helo in;
 Aw nem tak chuh ka za'i, na lung hun hei in,
 Ngaihdam neitai, na bat ka din tai.

[V4]
 3. Hukdampa lungsiet, lungsietna mak ahi,
 Kalvari di'n Lalchutphah nusie'n;
 Uain kithawk bangin Amah A thi tai,
 Kumkhuo'n Amin pakin genviel un.</lyrics>
</song>